    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "August 31, 1966",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "J. E. Hoover, F.B.I. Director",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Wash. D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Dear Sir:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "I am a member of \"Nicap\" and am very much",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "interested in U. F. O (Flying Saucers)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Several weeks ago a fellow employee received a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "letter (business) from Arizona with a stamp on the back (see",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "enclosed)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Being interested in U. F. O's I asked for the stamp",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "& sent $3.00 for the 12 issues of AFSCA.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Having received & read my first issue I feel it isn't",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "just what it appears on the surface. I can't say just why, but with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "my limited idea of how communists operate it strikes me it is backed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "by them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "My reason for writing this is that I consider myself",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "a true American, I am told my ancestors go back to a Gr Gr Gr",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "Grandmother who was an Indian Squaw & I'm proud of it. If, by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "writing for this AFSCA Report, my name could in anyway be aligned",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "with the communist party, I would like to know if there is any way I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "can get things straightened out.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "I may be all wrong about my interpretation of this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "report but I'd like to be sure since I expect I will get the other issues",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "as they come up.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "REC 98 62-73391-44",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
